#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_scale.rst:5
msgid "Copy Scale Constraint"
msgstr "Copy Scale Constraint 复制缩放约束"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_scale.rst:7
msgid ""
"The *Copy Scale* constraint forces its owner to have the same scale as "
"its target."
msgstr "复制缩放（Copy Rotation）约束强制约束对象获得目标的缩放。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_scale.rst:11
msgid ""
"Here we talk of *scale*, not of *size*! Indeed, you can have two "
"objects, one much bigger than the other, and yet both of them have the "
"same scale. This is also true with bones: in *Pose Mode*, they all have "
"a unitary scale when they are in rest position, represented by their "
"visible length."
msgstr ""
"在这里我们谈的是 *缩放*，而不是 *大小*！事实上，两个物体，一个比另一个大"
"很多，但两者可以有相同的缩放。这对于骨骼同样成立：在 *姿势模式* 下，静止"
"位置的骨骼有统一的缩放，代表它们的可见长度。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_scale.rst:19
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Options 选项"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_scale.rst:23
msgid "Copy Scale panel."
msgstr "复制缩放面板。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_scale.rst:27
msgid "Target"
msgstr "Target 目标"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_scale.rst:26
msgid ""
":ref:`ui-data-id` used to select the constraints target, and is not "
"functional (red state) when it has none."
msgstr ""
":ref:`ui-data-id` 用于选择约束目标，当它为空时此约束不起作用(红色状态)。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_scale.rst:30
msgid "X, Y, Z"
msgstr "X, Y, Z"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_scale.rst:30
msgid "These buttons control along which axes the scale is constrained."
msgstr "这些复选框用于选择被约束缩放的轴向。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_scale.rst:34
msgid "Offset"
msgstr "Offset 偏移量"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_scale.rst:33
msgid ""
"When enabled, this control allows the owner to be scaled (using its "
"current transform properties), relatively to its target's scale."
msgstr ""
"启用时，该控件允许约束对象(使用其当前的变换属性)相对于目标继续缩放。"

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_scale.rst:38
msgid "Additive"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/transform/copy_scale.rst:37
msgid ""
"Scale is a multiplicative quantity, so the *Offset* option by default "
"multiplies the owner scale by the target scale. With this option enabled "
"it instead adds them."
msgstr ""

